<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7799] LukeRequestHandler too slow when there are many fields</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7799</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;/admin/luke responds very slowly when there are many fields in the index.  The issue is with getFirstLiveDoc() spinning its wheels a lot to get the index flags.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12845629">SOLR-7799</key>
            <summary>LukeRequestHandler too slow when there are many fields</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
